ComicInfo.Summary:
With the Squire hot on the Terror's trail, Calie and Dark Cheshire venture to the ancient Valley of the Kings in search of the En Passant. As Calie uncovers clues to Wonderland's unique history, the Squire witnesses the Terror's capture!
With their enemy in the hands of pixies, Calie and the Squire must come up with a plan to rescue the creature they intend to destroy.
